snippet: There will be no sixth Olympic Games for Dara Torres. The 45-year-old 12-time Olympic medalist finished fourth in the 50-meter freestyle on Monday, an event where only the top two qualified.
abstract: There will be no sixth Olympic Games for Dara Torres. The 45-year-old 12-time Olympic medalist finished fourth in the 50-meter freestyle on Monday, an event where only the top two qualified.

headline.main: Torres Misses Out on Sixth Trip to the Olympics
